s Books\"</a>. <i>The New York Times</i>. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number\" title=\"International Standard Serial Number\">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.worldcat.org/issn/0362-4331\">0362-4331</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2017-05-26</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+New+York+Times&amp;rft.atitle=Childrens+Books&amp;rft.date=1972-05-07&amp;rft.issn=0362-4331&amp;rft.aulast=Schott&amp;rft.aufirst=Webster&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1972%2F05%2F07%2Farchives%2Fchildrens-books-what-do-yas-read.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFake+memoir\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-truthiness-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-truthiness_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Carr, David (30 January 2006). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2006/01/30/business/media/30carr.html?ex=1296277200&amp;en=1c0e8843da5b43d6&amp;ei=5088&amp;partner=rssnyt&amp;emc=rss\">\"How Oprahness Trumped Truthiness\"</a>. <i>The New York Times</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2007-10-05</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+New+York+Times&amp;rft.atitle=How+Oprahness+Trumped+Truthiness&amp;rft.date=2006-01-30&amp;rft.aulast=Carr&amp;rft.aufirst=David&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2006%2F01%2F30%2Fbusiness%2Fmedia%2F30carr.html%3Fex%3D1296277200%26en%3D1c0e8843da5b43d6%26ei%3D5088%26partner%3Drssnyt%26emc%3Drss&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFake+memoir\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">